4. Add an AnimationPlayer node to the scene and rename it to "PlayerAnim" or something similar.

5. Open the AnimationPlayer node in the Inspector. In the Animation Tree tab, add an animation clip called "walk_left" for walking left, "walk_right" for walking right, and "idle" for the idle animation.

6. In the Animation Clips tab, create keyframes for the animation clips by clicking the down arrow next to each clip and clicking "Add Keyframe". For the idle animation, add keyframes at 0 and 1 seconds.

